summary: Adds trees and plants to Solitude...
descriptionHtml:
DESCRIPTION:
This mod adds trees and plants to the city of Solitude only. 

INSTALLATION:
Copy file to data file in Skyrim dir and activate through Data Files in Launcher

UNISTALLATION:
Uncheck in Data files and or delete esm file

CONFLICTS:
This mod contains a Gildergreen tree and will conflict with mods that alter the tree to grow etc. 

NOTE:
I ran the mod and didnt notice a FPS drop but this may depend on your machine. I tried to make it Lite as possible without adding too many trees.

Also some plants were used that arnt technically from the Solitude region so its not lore-friendly but it looks way better with them in so they\'re there. Besides I noticed while doing this mod Bethesda did the same.

If there are any bugs or something is clipping just let me know as well as any suggestions
author: Mr Wes
